financial, professional& international insurance
the financial, professional& international insurance segment includes surety and financial liability coverages, which primarily
use credit-based underwriting processes, as well as property and casualty products that are primarily marketed on a domestic basis in the united kingdom, the republic of ireland and canada, and on an
