company's option, at a redemption price equal to the greater of (a)100% of the principal amount of senior notes to be redeemed or (b)the sum of the present values of the remaining
scheduled payments of principal and interest on the senior notes to be redeemed (exclusive of interest accrued to the date of redemption)
